_vn_ next span  _fd_ delete all filters  _hp_ set priority  _td_ diaries
_vp_ prev span  ^^                       ^^                 ^^
_vr_ reset      ^^                       ^^                 ^^
^^              ^^                       ^^                 ^^
"
